OL,5, Staff at Welsh language broadcaster S4C
OL,6, were left in tears after bullying at   
OL,7, work, a former employee has claimed.   
OL,9,FFormer director of communications Gwyn 
OL,10,FWilliams said he warned the board of   
OL,11,F"inappropriate behaviour" in April     
OL,12,F2022.                                  
OL,14,FIt comes after S4C chief executive Sian
OL,15,FDoyle was sacked following claims of a 
OL,16,F"toxic culture" at the organisation.   
OL,18,FS4C has been approached for a response 
OL,19,Fto Mr Williams' claims.                
